+/**
+ * Gas Town Bridge Plugin - Unified Cache System
+ *
+ * High-performance caching with:
+ * - O(1) LRU cache with Map + doubly linked list
+ * - WeakMap for formula AST caching (GC-friendly)
+ * - Result memoization for expensive operations
